{You dealt this hand.  

Of course you open 1\S. Partner responds 2\C. What is your next bid? 

Partner has shown at least 11 points and you are forced to bid again. Since the \Hs rank below \Ss you can bid them with your minimum hand. Apparently that is just what partner wanted to hear since he jumps to 3NT which you happily pass.}

